    dc:description "Fig. 2. Mandible close-ups of workers from the elegantula-complex in the Strumigenys leptothrix-group. A–B. S. intermedia sp. nov. (TT01353). C. S. elegantula (Terayama & Kubota, 1989) from Hong Kong (RHL00290). D. S. jacobsoni Menozzi, 1939 from Vietnam (ANTWEB1011973)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10148815/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10148843>
    dc:description "Fig. 15. Workers of Strumigenys cf. doydeei sp. nov. in full-face, profile and dorsal views. A–C. Worker from Thailand (CASENT0285186, taken by Cong Liu). D–F. Worker from Yunnan, mainland China (CASENT0715043, taken by Takumi Uchima, Environmental Science Section, OIST)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10148843/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10148845>
    dc:description "Fig. 16. Workers of Strumigenys elegantula (Terayama & Kubota, 1989) in full-face, profile and dorsal views. A–C. Worker from Hong Kong (ANTWEB1009804). D–F. Worker from Thailand (ANTWEB1011998)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10148845/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

